applicable industry standards and regulations.

---

INDUSTRY STANDARDS COMPLIANCE

This software implements calculations based on:
- API Standard 521 (Flare Radiation)
- API RP 14E (Erosional Velocity)
- Darcy-Weisbach Equation (Pressure Drop)
- Beggs-Brill Correlation (Two-Phase Flow)
- Other recognized industry standards

Users are responsible for ensuring compliance with:
- Local regulations and standards
- Company-specific requirements
- Safety protocols and procedures
- Environmental regulations

